# Documentation and Configuration Standards

## Package.json Structure
Reference [package.json](mdc:package.json) for current configuration:
- React 18.2.0 with React Scripts 5.0.1
- Standard Create React App scripts (start, build, test, eject)
- Browserslist configuration for broad compatibility

## Documentation Guidelines
- Use clear, descriptive headings
- Include code examples with proper syntax highlighting
- Reference actual project files using mdc: links
- Maintain consistency with existing documentation style

## Metadata Requirements
- Proper HTML meta tags in [index.html](mdc:public/index.html)
- Descriptive title and description
- Appropriate viewport and theme-color settings

## Git Configuration
- [.gitignore](mdc:.gitignore) excludes node_modules
- Standard React project ignore patterns
- Keep repository clean of build artifacts
